<s> Windows: It's now possible to change the value of the user's preferences directory.  </s>
<s> To do so, edit the win-thot.rc  </s>
<s> and add a variable called APP_HOME in the [amaya] section.  </s>
<s> The value of this variable should be the path to directory.  </s>
<s> This is interesting if you want to install Amaya in an NFS drive, but store the user's preferences locally.  </s>
<s> In-reply-to: Your message of Fri, 24 Nov 2000 16:27:58 -0500."  </s>
<s> The file is in the Amaya distribution at Amaya\config\win-thot.rc  </s>
